            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1470.297" end="x">They also were burned if they had incriminated themselves greatly against the Hitler regime, they were also burned. When we arrived we were all lined up four abreast and we were transported away on foot not anymore in "automobiles" toward the inside of the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
