                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1503.288" end="x">What is a <a class="term" href="#vothG_mussulman">Mussulman</a>?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1504.454" end="x">A <a class="term" href="#vothG_mussulman">Mussulman</a> you know, to look like a <a class="term" href="#vothG_mussulman">Mussulman</a> meant a very emaciated a person who looked in <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a> very emaciated was called a <a class="term" href="#vothG_mussulman">Mussulman</a>, and he already had no right to live.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1513.678" end="x">H-um.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1514.475" end="x">And we haven't seen them anymore. We arrived at two o'clock in <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a>. We were led into special <a class="term" href="#vothG_block">blocks</a>, so-called barracks, erected of wood. As soon as we entered there came the ruler of <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a>: quick, in a hurry, go on in the German language. "Strip completely," and in a minute one had to be completely undressed, and soon their clubs were striking our backs and we were driven into what they called the washroom, to bathe. At the bath they sheared off our hair everywhere.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
