            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1547.412" end="x">This was done by Jews, well-seasoned, old prisoners. French Jews, Belgian Jews, those who have managed to achieve a certain post, a certain rank.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1556.229" end="x">Yes.</span>
