            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1704.080" end="x">K—-L that means concentration camp, that one should not be able to escape. And they led us to the place so-called <a class="placename" href="#vothC10" type="camp">Birkenau</a>. <a class="placename" href="#vothC10" type="camp">Birkenau</a> was called the quarantine, that meant to prepare us so we could then be transferred for <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a> for work.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
