            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="1925.362" end="x">Per day. This was the food given . . . but until one could push himself forward to [get] this food, one could lose half of his health. I spent in <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a>, in <a class="placename" href="#vothC10" type="camp">Birkenau</a>, three months. After three months there came a commission from the Krupp factory . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
