            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2031.651" end="x">We have not been doing every day anything [definite], either we were going to carry rocks, or we were ordered . . .</span>
        </li>
