            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2035.912" end="x">From the railroad station, because the railroad station was also in the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>. There was everything in the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
