            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2586.032" end="x">Men only, seventeen hundred men. We got into the washroom, and there stood Ukrainians, also internees, and with cold, such what do they call it, cold hoses with which one pours water . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="2599.459" end="x">Yes.</span>
        </li>
