            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2599.723" end="x">They poured water all over us. The windows were open and soon, momentarily, people started to die.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="2605.428" end="x">Why?</span>
