            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2808.229" end="x">They made them, they were manufactured, they manufactured them in Germany without limit, the factories produced such special prisoners' clothing, that is for those who were under arrest . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="2813.750" end="x">H-um.</span>
