            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2968.648" end="x">But coming out of the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> we observed that a change has taken place. It was the 28th of April.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="2973.542" end="x">We observed the change in the fact that the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> men we were not led any more by <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> men, by Jews without arms.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
