            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Udel Stopnitsky</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="3087.521" end="x">Nothing, there were no more <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> in sight at all, they were not seen any more. Because the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> was preparing already for the retreat, to run away. And so I was lying there [I am not sure of this verb] until the 8th of May. The 8th of May there came news that <a class="placename" href="#vothL298">Prague</a> was taken by the Red Army.</span>
