            <span class="utterance" who="stopnitskyU" start="3331.345" end="x">From the ten, that was all. The two brothers departed right away for the land of Israel. We did not want any part any more of the pale [he uses the Hebrew word goles which really means "exile," this refers to the exile of the Jews from Palestine about two thousand years ago], we saw that the pale was burning [the word "burning" was used commonly to indicate <a class="term" href="#vothG_pogrom">pogroms</a> and anti-Semitic violence.]</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
