            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Flossenb&#195;rg, Germany<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                Concentration camp built in May 1938 by the SS in the Oberpfalz region of Bavaria. Between 1938 and liberation in April 1945, more than 96,000 prisoners passed through Flossenb&#195;rg. About 28,000 died there.
            </div>
